column4: NSLOCTEXT("[1A198BCA46A98AB2EFB586AE99F8ECFE]", "A0EC33544F508D9A35D0DFBDCC01E6D7", "Oh, {Player}, {Partner} you came. Look at this great File City Arena. Cool, huh!")
NSLOCTEXT("[1A198BCA46A98AB2EFB586AE99F8ECFE]", "CD60182C4527CD99F169CC90DD306D0E", "Soon contestants and fans will fill this up. You will also bring joy to the fans, right?!")
NSLOCTEXT("[1A198BCA46A98AB2EFB586AE99F8ECFE]", "0088437140AEDDCC4DD08FA4B64EB48D", "They\'ll prepare money and prizes for tournament winners. You got nothing to lose.")
NSLOCTEXT("[1A198BCA46A98AB2EFB586AE99F8ECFE]", "C821960B4716392160DF1A96459C176C", "For details on the tournament, check out the machine there.")
NSLOCTEXT("[1A198BCA46A98AB2EFB586AE99F8ECFE]", "2DA5C1F9463B6D8B7779EF88D0C15C9B", "I\'m glad you came. Do you wanna enter the tournament?")
NSLOCTEXT("[1A198BCA46A98AB2EFB586AE99F8ECFE]", "2F7C88724D044C6737D531A41BBDA62E", "Once inside, at start time, go down the left stairs in order to compete in battle.")
NSLOCTEXT("[1A198BCA46A98AB2EFB586AE99F8ECFE]", "AA00D8744549CC2D407A33A03BF7086C", "Registration is free. You can register for only today\'s and tommorrow\'s competition.")
NSLOCTEXT("[1A198BCA46A98AB2EFB586AE99F8ECFE]", "AC3CCFEF4B15ADF1FBC558BAFCD9EB60", "However, for that day\'s competition, you have to register by 10:00.")
NSLOCTEXT("[1A198BCA46A98AB2EFB586AE99F8ECFE]", "2C5A190B49D7825F26CB058F0FEAE13B", "You can check the schedule five days ahead, so check it and make your plans.")
NSLOCTEXT("[1A198BCA46A98AB2EFB586AE99F8ECFE]", "96E7327946CDEA8D739D8D88699588D0", "The competitions in red mean you that you can\'t take part.")
NSLOCTEXT("[1A198BCA46A98AB2EFB586AE99F8ECFE]", "758A1BFD474AC4D933727D97F28805DF", "But press the start button to check what it\'s about.")
NSLOCTEXT("[1A198BCA46A98AB2EFB586AE99F8ECFE]", "918CF3694DE461186873958C26A5F4A8", "Well, that\'s about it for registration. Do you want to enter?")
